These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
House: tower, futuristic, cottage, art-deco, palace
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, collecting, rock-climbing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
6. the tower house is in the middle##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| House   | futuristic | cottage | tower | palace | art-deco |
| Hobby   | video-games    | hiking | collecting     | rock-climbing       | puzzles  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, alhambra, blend, havana, ritmeester
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, lilac, chestnut, red, azure
1. the havana-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the cain-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
4. the cain-smoker is in the middle##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is the person who likes chestnut##1
6. the person who likes azure is the ritmeester-smoker##1
7. the person who likes red is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Cigar      | alhambra | blend | cain | havana | ritmeester |
| Color   | chestnut  | red   | grey       | lilac    | azure   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, analyst, writer, doctor, videographer
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, aconite, rose, poppy
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the doctor is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the journalist is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
4. the writer is on the far left##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
6. the analyst is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Job        | writer | doctor | analyst | journalist | videographer |
| Flower   | marigold  | begonia      | poppy | aconite | rose      |

