.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, january, september, december, may
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, folk, punk, funk, salsa
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday   | december    | june        | september | january | may |
| Music-Genre     | soul | funk | salsa  | folk   | punk |

