.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, hip-hop, techno, rock, ambient
5 different games are played: chess, monopoly, snooker, whist, domino
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the fan of techno##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the fan of ambient##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
5. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of pop##1
6. the person playing domino is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Music-Genre    | techno   | pop     | hip-hop   | rock         | ambient |
| Game   | chess | whist | snooker | domino | monopoly     |

