.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, italian, american, polish
5 different games are played: backgammon, poker, chess, domino, snooker
1. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing chess is the italian##1
5. the polish is on the right of the chinese##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Nationality       | american   | italian   | chinese | polish | brazilian |
| Game   | poker | chess | domino   | snooker | backgammon       |

