.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
House: wooden, art-deco, townhouse, cape-cod, victorian
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, board-games, gardening, filmmaking, rock-climbing
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the wooden house##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the wooden house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| House     | art-deco   | townhouse  | victorian      | wooden | cape-cod     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | gardening | board-games | hiking   | rock-climbing |

