.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, soy-milk, juice, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, metal, pop, techno, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of techno##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of pop##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage     | tea | fanta       | hot-chocolate | juice | soy-milk    |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | classical | pop  | metal     | jazz |

