.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, cat, turtle, rat, horse
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, lily, amaryllis, begonia
1. the person who growslily is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the owner of the horse is the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Pet         | rat | chinchilla | turtle | horse | cat |
| Flower   | lily       | amaryllis   | begonia         | daisy   | bellflower   |

