2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who likes purple##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
