.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald, ebony, grey, amber
5 different games are played: backgammon, whist, billiard, canasta, monopoly
1. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person who likes grey is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Color    | lavender | grey          | ebony    | amber | emerald  |
| Game   | billiard  | monopoly | backgammon | canasta | whist |

