.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, action, documentary, martial-arts, sports
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, march, september, february, january
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | romance      | martial-arts | action | sports |
| Birthday     | february  | march | may     | january     | september  |

