.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, tram, trike, van, taxi
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, cranberry, peas, strawberry, cherry
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Transport      | taxi | trike | jet-ski      | van | tram      |
| Food   | cranberry  | strawberry       | asparagus | cherry  | peas |

