.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, climbing, volleyball, surfing, skateboarding
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, mystery, sports, satire, western
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Sport           | surfing     | skateboarding | cricket | volleyball  | climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | western               | mystery     | sports | satire |

