.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, montecristo, cain, bluemaster, tiparillo
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, water, hot-chocolate, mirinda
1. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Cigar   | montecristo | tiparillo | cain | oliveros | bluemaster |
| Beverage           | mirinda | hot-chocolate  | juice    | almond-milk  | water   |

 